     Just wanted to praise the Bus Depot.... I've been looking everywhere for
several parts and I found them at www.busdepot.com. I made my order last week,
and it was promptly shipped! Thanks!!!

My only complaint is that... the box clearly stated: "KEEP REFRIGERATED" in
