that will affect my ignition lock, and the tail-lights lenses. I guess I won't
know until after I install them.

Ok, that was probably really lame, but I've had a couple of gin and tonics,
and as far as I'm concerned, that's the funniest thing I've heard all day.


Thanks Bus Depot!


